Method Detail

onBasicMeasurementFinished

void onBasicMeasurementFinished(int currentMessageCount,
                                int statusCode,
                                java.math.BigDecimal bodyWeight)
Receives the data from a BasicMeasurementFinished event.

Parameters:
currentMessageCount - The value of the message counter when this event was triggered. Useful for correlating multiple events. Rollover: the count is an integer incremented by one each message, rolling through the entire integer range.
statusCode - The RequestStatusCode defining the result of the measurement task.
bodyWeight - Body weight value, null = 'Invalid', also null if request was unsuccessful. Units: Kg.
